        <section>
            <p><sourcexml>leg:heading</sourcexml> becomes <targetxml>heading</targetxml> in target.
                
                </p>
        </section>
        <example>
            <title>Mapping of <sourcexml>leg:heading</sourcexml></title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;leg:level id="LECOEXTE.ACT.1"&gt;
        &lt;leg:level-vrnt leveltype="act" subdoc="true" toc-caption="LEY DE COMERCIO EXTERIOR"&gt;
                &lt;leg:heading&gt;
                    &lt;title&gt;LEY DE COMERCIO EXTERIOR&lt;/title&gt;
                &lt;/leg:heading&gt;
                .....
        &lt;/leg:level-vrnt&gt;
&lt;/leg:level&gt;

      </codeblock>
            <b>becomes</b>
            <codeblock>

&lt;primlaw:level xml:id="LECOEXTE.ACT.1" leveltype="act" includeintoc="true" alternatetoccaption="LEY DE COMERCIO EXTERIOR"&gt;
    &lt;heading&gt;
        &lt;title&gt;LEY DE COMERCIO EXTERIOR&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;heading&gt;
    .....
&lt;/primlaw:level&gt;
    
      </codeblock>
        </example> 
       
       <note>If <sourcexml>leg:heading</sourcexml> is having <sourcexml>glp:note/refpt</sourcexml>
